{"tid":1538181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武係前線擋子彈，和理非可以做啲乜？「和理非網上宣戰指引」","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:26.000Z","uid":276533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6b6caeb3fc9976d1aa5cf1d7ef5a706a94668f","tid":1538181,"uid":276533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"大家有冇發現呢排大部分嘅勇武都唔係比警察追到，而係俾人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">篤灰</span></strong>，以致被捕？<br />\n其實我做咗幾個月Facebook打手，我完全明白藍絲點解咁有勇氣，面對俾人圍毆起底，都要篤灰，就係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋覺得自己背後好多人支持佢呀！！</span></strong>其實有常識都知，依家黃比藍嘅比例，大約7：3。<br />\n點解佢哋咁有信心？因為黃絲同藍絲都有一個共同點，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係大家都中意打飛機</span></span></strong>，淨係follow啱自己政見嘅Page。試問大家有冇follow藍絲post，研究佢哋嘅思維？無呀！我知大家見到藍絲post嬲到想掟手機，但係大家有無諗過其實我哋可以係<strong>網上開戰線</strong>，幫啲勇武？如上所說，藍絲一開Facebook，留個垃圾comment，就有成班廢老喺度like，佢哋梗係有信心啦！所以我哋必須係呢方面攻擊佢哋，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>令佢地打飛機都冇得打！</strong></span>以下係幾個建議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 開個假Facebook account，一齊做五毛</span></span><br />\n其實好簡單，開個account，用幅長輩圖做propic，然後follow晒所有藍絲Page，跟住瘋狂咁洗版，做文宣。可以點洗版？有幾個方法：<br />\nA. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>扮廢老</strong></span>，懶叻喺度評論時事，但係暗裡批評黑警，鬧鳩林鄭。<br />\n<em>「其實我都想支持警察執法，但係佢哋的確有濫用暴力，我個孫睇到喊晒 etc etc」</em>相信大家都明點做<br />\nB. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>文宣</strong></span>，用圖片，用理據，好似耶撚咁傳教。我知好多藍絲都係弱智，無邏輯，但係其中一定有啲淺藍和受教育人士，所以要俾佢哋見到平時見唔到既野<br />\nC. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>搞分化</strong></span>。扮大陸人，扮深藍，然後和藍絲割蓆，話佢哋一文都不值。<br />\n<em>「其实蓝丝对于咱們大陆人来说，只是一班贱民，当香港正式回归中国，连普通话都不懂的蓝丝只会被唾弃！」</em><br />\nD. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勇武派</strong></span>，姐係用粗口破罵，但唔太建議，因為佢哋都習慣晒俾人屌。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲Page：<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">幫港出聲，港人講地，向香港警察致敬，點新聞，時聞香港，所有建制派議員</span></ins> etc. （仲有好多，自己搵）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. Like國際新聞Page，用香港人聲音蓋過五毛</span></span><br />\n呼籲所有中學大學生，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">like晒所有英文新聞Page</span></strong>，又可以學英文，又可以支持香港。點解要咁做？因為太多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">五毛</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">鬼佬左膠</span></strong>。睇吓下面BBC：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecEX1g3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecEX1g3.png&h=4da84666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為外國人一定支持香港，佢哋其實對香港完全冇認知，只係覺得BBC反共，所以不可信。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中學生，你哋罷課，記住不罷學，唔該練下你哋嘅英文</strong></span>，向外國人解釋香港發生乜事。<br />\n呢個最好唔好用假account，因為要話俾外國人知，我哋係香港發生嘅事係真架，同埋大部份港人都支持示威。<br />\n<br />\n新聞page：<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">BBC News, CNN, Reuters, SCMP, New York Times, Washington Post, The Guardian, The Independent, TIME</span></ins> etc.<br />\n<br />\n請和理非，各位巴打絲打，唔好再懶啦，好無？勇武日日係度比人打，點解我哋咁簡單嘅嘢都做唔到？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">搭巴士，食飯，訓覺前，去藍絲page講一講，分一分，鬧一鬧，屌一屌</span></span></strong>，已經幫左勇武好多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我約定大家，除咗係煲底見，都係網上戰線和大家相見，互相like下，心心react下，將藍絲page殺到片甲不留，好無？</strong></span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 唔好抄我以上既例子，我哋唔係bot，係有血有肉嘅人，請用番自己嘅文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305d831c471cb474b7e25110b0a2c5ab8025f494","tid":1538181,"uid":276533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfqHs1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfqHs1o.png&h=3a68b534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"522c314c1fa6690dba7f710e8a48ff716caf117f","tid":1538181,"uid":22919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"認同請分享"},{"pid":"400c9eb26771444b0cef49b99b41b1e6fe07b885","tid":1538181,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"adda4450c92af1af7023744d956c5467b4b5eb8a","tid":1538181,"uid":276533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"我要係藍絲Page淨係見到黃絲同分化藍絲嘅comment呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d3c796cc26544bfb4c0397d67ac48e02299d9b","tid":1538181,"uid":276533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/koFMah6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkoFMah6.jpg&h=e7665f87&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}